data.description: The search is finally over! This lovely home in the active Adult Community of Sunland Village is the one! The cozy front porch welcomes you into this charming home with a spacious Livingroom, ceiling fans throughout, upgraded wood like flooring, and a soothing color palette. Cooking is a delight in the eat-in kitchen, featuring built-in appliances, gleaming granite counters, white cabinetry, refrigerator & pantry. The oversized interior laundry comes complete with washer/dryer.  And let's not forget about the well-sized bonus room offering additional living space. Two large bedrooms with oversized closets and an upgraded bathroom add to the appeal of this wonderful home. Large private backyard with paver patio and a shade tree is a great spot to enjoy our cooler AZ mornings.
